{"tid":942001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"櫻花妹色氣Cos初音未來！畫面震撼推特…上萬網友熱轉：不能只有我看到","createTime":"2018-12-15T09:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T13:26:39.000Z","uid":212399,"like":869,"dislike":102,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"3f07e36324ea0d03675e1da9f482962eba0459ec","tid":942001,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3764/3764903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3764%2F3764903.jpg&h=733a160e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美瑠喜時常在推特上分享Cosplay照片。（圖／翻攝自美瑠喜kuchipatchi85推特）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n畫面超美我不敢看！日本一位女模Coser時常扮演喜愛的動漫角色，穿上華麗造型，在推特上發表最新的cosplay照片。最近她扮演虛擬女歌手「初音未來」（初音ミク），照片曝光，導致眾多網友紛紛「噴了」，超過1萬1000人按讚、9千多人轉載分享「不能只有我看到」。<br />\n日本知名女網紅Coser「美瑠喜」（MIRUKI）在推特上分享Cosplay「初音未來」的照片，她在文內表示，這是充滿「色氣」的初音未來，就如群星歌姬維納斯（Venus）。<br />\n透過照片可以看到，美瑠喜頂著一頭灰白頭髮，直接綻放她傲人的美胸，穿著緊身的初音服飾對著鏡子自拍，大膽露出「恥線」，身體三點甚至若隱若現，完全不在意他人的眼光，相當有自信秀出美麗照片，誠意十足。<br />\n網友看到照片後紛紛留言：「看起來真可愛」、「感謝您辛苦工作」、「非常專業的打扮」、「這是驚人的裝扮」；不過也有網友調侃：「自殺炸彈嗎」、「會自爆」、「突然想吃泡麵了」、「我覺得生命縮短了483天」、「畫面太美只好努力瞇眼」等，還有超壞的酸民幫忙修圖。<br />\n▼網友幫美瑠喜修Cosplay照片。（圖／翻攝自美瑠喜kuchipatchi85推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3764/3764907.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3764%2F3764907.jpg&h=f77018f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3764/3764904.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3764%2F3764904.jpg&h=79ff1f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3764/3764906.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3764%2F3764906.jpg&h=3bda186a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3764/3764905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3764%2F3764905.jpg&h=b5551f89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181215/1331489.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181215%2F1331489.htm&d=JLp0aZeKgaDJxHa8AUPXkQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=00cd975d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181215/1331489.htm</a>"},{"pid":"46c3eb615c2b3cf2ba3253e7badfd9c9ec62da92","tid":942001,"uid":59278,"like":282,"dislike":2,"score":280,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"畀你呃撚咗入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc702484fa95b65f946516aa37db1b6bd83ecf6a","tid":942001,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a43fa18ed28875394bd58c9c02f9c30326136ad","tid":942001,"uid":22585,"like":276,"dislike":0,"score":276,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"不能只有我看到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b32a0be3815388a1f208c80a022c54b9442c6c","tid":942001,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23af9ae08533efadb231c43a2cfdfbc0045185bf","tid":942001,"uid":17566,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"不能只有我看到系列 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cc2817fb4ac2742f8795414600c6b6dcf5bd05","tid":942001,"uid":186934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:01:11.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dadbcdcb4c89c7faf62abd641ecc784365f5c97","tid":942001,"uid"